20confirmed%20the%20layoffs%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20the%20reduction%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Boptimize%20operational%20efficiency%20and%20revenue%20growth%20in%20our%20key%20verticals%20of%20beauty%20and%20fashion%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Goop%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20second%20known%20round%20of%20cuts%20this%20year.%20In%20September%2C%20the%20newsletter-turned-e-commerce%20site%20laid%20off%2018%25%20of%20its%20216-person%20staff%2C%20or%20about%2040%20people.%20The%20cuts%20included%20at%20least%20one%20member%20of%20the%20company's%20C-suite%2C%20CMO%20Lauren%20Johnston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20last%20month%2C%20actor%20and%20Goop%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Paltrow%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwwd.com%2Fbeauty-industry-news%2Fbeauty-features%2Fgwyneth-paltrow-launches-goop-mascara-1236429700%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWWD%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20following%20the%20first%20round%20of%20layoffs%2C%20Goop%20was%20%26quot%3Bback%20in%20growth%20mode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Goop%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20provide%20specific%20revenue%20figures%20but%20said%20revenue%20grew%20year%20over%20year%20in%202023%20and%20was%20on%20track%20to%20grow%20again%20in%202024.%20Goop%20Beauty%20revenue%20is%20up%2021%25%20over%20last%20year%2C%20and%20G.%20Label%20revenue%20is%20up%2045%25%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20say%20if%20the%20company%20is%20profitable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20those%20layoffs%20were%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20restructuring%2C%20adding%20that%20Goop%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20at%20times%20sold%20everything%20from%20vitamins%20to%20home%20goods%20%E2%80%94%20was%20doubling%20down%20on%20beauty%2C%20food%2C%20and%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20company%20hired%20consultants%20from%20a%20company%20called%20WestView%20to%20streamline%20business%2C%20the%20company%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3