0pet%20owners%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20animal-friendly%20offices%20and%20co-working%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20often%20saw%20dogs%20hanging%20out%20beneath%20pub%20tables%2C%20in%20line%20with%20their%20owners%20at%20banks%2C%20or%20even%20quietly%20enjoying%20a%20movie%20at%20the%20cinema.%20We%20also%20found%20that%20hotels%20and%20Airbnbs%20in%20the%20UK%20were%20typically%20more%20accepting%20of%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20likes%20to%20pet%20other%20people's%20dogs%2C%20it%20was%20nice%20to%20have%20plenty%20of%20opportunities%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20long%20for%20pharmacies%20that%20only%20sell%20health%20products.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pharmacy%20shelves%20filled%20with%20medicine%20at%20Boots%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6363e6ceff27460018ed6d22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pharmacies%20I%20went%20to%20in%20the%20UK%20mainly%20sold%20medicine.%3Cp%3EJames%20Copeland%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20US%20pharmacies%2C%20customers%20often%20need%20to%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20store%20to%20find%20pharmacists%2C%20medicine%2C%20and%20health%20products%20like%20sunscreen%20and%20vitamins.%20Other%20retail%20space%20is%20typically%20devoted%20to%20snacks%2C%20candy%2C%20cosmetics%2C%20gadgets%2C%20and%20gifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20pharmacies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-about-living-in-50-countries-photos-2022-1%5C%22%3EI%20encountered%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20stocked%20almost%20exclusively%20with%20health%20items.%20I%20miss%20not%20having%20to%20wade%20through%20aisles%20of%20candy%20and%20hair%20gel%20to%20find%20cold%20medicine%20when%20I%20need%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20miss%20smaller%20portion%20sizes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20