%20a%20joke%20about%20Puerto%20Rico.%20Then%20Biden's%20gaffe.%20And%20it%20only%20continued%20from%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBoth%20campaigns%20are%20trying%20to%20generate%20breakthrough%20moments%20to%20their%20benefit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20a%20rally%20in%20Wausau%2C%20Wisconsin%20on%20Monday%2C%20Sen.%20JD%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%20called%20on%20Americans%20to%20toughen%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20we%20have%20to%20stop%20getting%20so%20offended%20at%20every%20little%20thing%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%20I'm%20just%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20so%20over%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vance%2C%20the%20GOP's%20vice%20presidential%20nominee.%20%26quot%3BOur%20country%20was%20built%20by%20frontiersmen%20who%20conquered%20the%20wilderness.%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20restore%20the%20greatness%20of%20American%20civilization%20if%20we%20get%20offended%20at%20every%20little%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20about%20comedian%20Tony%20Hinchliffe's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-madison-square-garden-rally-overshadow-economy-puerto-rico-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoke%20about%20Puerto%20Rico%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bfloating%20island%20of%20garbage%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20Trump%20rally%20the%20previous%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Tuesday%2C%20Vance%20himself%20seemed%20offended%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJDVance%2Fstatus%2F1851419418842034332%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20to%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20weigh%20in%20on%20a%20clip%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20responding%20to%20the%20Hinchcliffe%20controversy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20appearing%20to%20refer%20to%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20supporters%20as%20garbage.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20disgusting%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20excuse%20for%20this.%20I%20hope%20Americans%20reject%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%20week%20of%20the%202024%20presidential%20election%2C%20fury%20and%20indignation%20have%20been%20the%20name%20of%20the%20game%2C%20with%20one%20outrage%20cycle%20leading%20almost%20seamlessly%20into%20the%20next%20%E2%80%94%20and%20both%20sides%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20moment%20at%20each%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHinchliffe's%20Puerto%20Rico%20joke%20spawned%20the%20initial%20news%20cycle%20(and%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20a%20new%20digital%20ad%20from%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris'%20campaign).%20Then%20came%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-biden-maga-supporters-puerto-rico-election-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiden's%20own%20gaffe%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20(the%20White%20House%20has%20insisted%20that%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20Hinchliffe's%20%26quot%3Bdemonization%20of%20Latinos.%26quot%3B)%20Seizing%20on%20the%20moment%2C%20Trump%20climbed%20into%20a%20garbage%20truck%20branded%20with%20his%20campaign's%20logo%20in%20Wisconsin%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20a%20rally%20soon%20after%2C%20clad%20in%20the%20bright-orange%20vest%20of%20a%20garbage%20truck%20operator%2C%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fatrupar%2Fstatus%2F1851778142580384209%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20would%20protect%20women%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20the%20women%20like%20it%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20Harris%20and%20her%20campaign%20quickly%20sought%20to%20amplify%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKamalaHQ%2Fstatus%2F1852099368288919577%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecasting%20the%20remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20women's%20agency%20and%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Trump%20and%20his%20allies%20got%20their%20own%20talking%20point%20on%20women%20when%20billionaire%20investor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-mark-cu