0are%20those%20who%20love%20Halloween%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20Christmas%20decorations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20say%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20like%20it%2C%20just%20don't%20look.%20It's%20not%20hurting%20anybody%2C%20and%20it's%20in%20my%20own%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295fce0f7-6ac7-4f61-961f-d593b0484449%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20of%20Christmas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMarket-research%20firm%20Prophecy%20Market%20Insights%20projected%20that%20the%20Christmas-decoration%20industry%20will%20grow%20from%20%248.45%20billion%20in%202024%20to%20%2413.04%20billion%20by%202034.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20National%20Retail%20Federation%20survey%20conducted%20by%20Prosper%20Insights%20%26amp%3B%20Analytics%2C%20this%20year%20the%20typical%20consumer%20will%20spend%20an%20average%20of%20%24902%20on%20items%20including%20gifts%2C%20food%2C%20decorations%2C%20and%20other%20seasonal%20items.%20The%20%24902%20figure%20is%20a%20record%20high%2C%20up%20%2425%20from%202023%20and%20a%20jump%20of%20%2416%20from%20the%20previous%20record%2C%20set%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20factor%20contributing%20to%20the%20increase%20may%20be%20that%20retailers%20are%20stocking%20holiday%20items%20and%20offering%20sales%20earlier%20in%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20winter%20holiday%20season%20has%20historically%20started%20at%20Halloween%2C%20but%20it's%20shifted%20sooner%2C%20said%20Sky%20Canaves%2C%20a%20retail%20and%20e-commerce%20analyst%20at%20EMARKETER.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanaves%20said%20the%20trend%20began%20with%20Amazon%20moving%20Prime%20Day%20to%20October%20in%202020%20and%20officially%20establishing%20an%20annual%20October%20sale%20by%202022%2C%20prompting%20other%20major%20retailers%20to%20follow.%20Now%2C%20Amazon%20Prime%20Day%2C%20held%20on%20October%208%20and%209%20this%20year%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20kickoff%20to%20the%20holiday%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetailers%20used%20to%20wait%20until%20Halloween%20had%20passed%20to%20put%20out%20the%20Christmas%20decor%2C%20now%20we're%20more%20likely%20to%20see%20Halloween%20and%20Christmas%20sections%20side-by-side%2C%26quot%3B%20Canaves%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20jarring%20at%20first%2C%20but%20shoppers%20are%20getting%20used%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220b95d56-ad5c-4a0f-9735-97f07843a7a0%5C%22%3EHer%20Christmas%20aesthetic%20isn't%20just%20red%20and%20green%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBolio%20shops%20for%20decorations%20from%20At%20Home%2C%20HomeGoods%2C%20T.J.%20Maxx%2C%20and%20Michaels.%20She%20also%20browses%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20and%20thrift%20stores%20for%20unique%20finds%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20pink%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPink%20is%20my%20favorite%20color%2C%20so%20I%20get%20excited%20to%20find%20decorations%20that%20aren't%20the%20traditional%20Christmas%20colors%20like%20red%20and%20green%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20pink%20gingerbread%20houses%2C%20trees%2C%20and%20nutcrackers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20draped%20her%20shelves%20with%20string%20lights%20and%20lined%20each%20surface%20with%20artificial%20snow%2C%20placing%20miniature%20Christmas%20trees%20and%20signs%20proclaiming%20%26quot%3BJoy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBelieve%26quot%3B%20amid%20the%20books.%20A%20snowman%20cup%20sits%20on%20a%20shelf%20beside%20her%20copy%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodreads.com%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F58724801-the-bodyguard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Bodyguard%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20by%20Katherine%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffall-thanksgiving-decor-shopping-target-vs-anthropologie-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecorating%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebrings%20great%20joy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20sit%20in%20the%20room%2C%20I%20feel%20very%20calm%20and%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20peace.%26quot%3B