Person%20Suffering%3A%20Delhi%20Pollution%20Survey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20skyrocketing%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%20-%20which%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20the%20highest%20pollutant%20levels%20in%20the%20world%20the%20day%20after%20Diwali%20-%20is%20directly%20impacting%20people's%20health%2C%20with%2069%25%20of%20families%20in%20the%20capital%20and%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20reporting%20at%20least%20one%20person%20suffering%2C%20a%20survey%20has%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAQI%20(Air%20Quality%20Index)%20on%20the%20night%20of%20Diwali%20on%20Thursday%20also%20reached%20999%2C%20which%20is%20the%20highest%20recordable%20level%2C%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20Delhi%20and%20NCR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%2C%20by%20LocalCircles%2C%20which%20received%20over%2021%2C000%20responses%20from%20residents%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Noida%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20Faridabad%20and%20Ghaziabad%2C%20revealed%20that%2069%25%20of%20families%20have%20one%20or%20more%20members%20with%20sore%20throat%20or%20cough%2C%2062%25%20have%20at%20least%20one%20member%20feeling%20a%20burning%20sensation%20in%20their%20eyes%20due%20to%20rising%20levels%20of%20pollution%20and%2046%25%20have%20someone%20with%20a%20running%20nose%20or%20congestion.%20Several%20respondents%20reported%20more%20than%20one%20symptom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20with%20breathing%20difficulty%20or%20asthma%20were%20reported%20by%2031%25%2C%20headache%20by%2031%25%2C%20anxiety%20and%20or%20difficulty%20concentrating%20by%2023%25%20and%20difficulty%20sleeping%20by%2015%25.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%2031%25%20also%20said%20no%20one%20in%20their%20families%20had%20any%20issues%20at%20all%20because%20of%20pollution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20similar%20survey%20was%20conducted%20on%20October%2019%2C%20days%20after%20GRAP%20(graded%20response%20action%20plan)-1%20was%20imposed%20on%20Delhi%20and%20there%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20symptoms%20in%20two%20weeks.%20The%20percentage%20of%20people%20with%20sore%20throat%20and%20or%20cough%20went%20up%20from%2036%25%20at%20the%20time%20to%2069%25%20as%20of%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Just%20Live%20With%20It'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%2023%25%20of%20respondents%20will%20use%20air%20purifiers%20to%20see%20them%20through%20this%20phase%20of%20very%20high%20pollution%20and%20an%20equal%20number%20said%20they%20will%20just%20live%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E15%25%20stated%20that%20they%20plan%20to%20carry%20on%20with%20their%20routine%20activity%20and%20wear%20a%20mask%20when%20outdoors%2C%20the%20same%20number%20said%20they%20would%20do%20this%20while%20increasing%20consumption%20of%20immunity-boosting%20food%20or%20drinks%2C%20and%20the%20same%20percentage%20also%20said%20they%20plan%20to%20travel%20for%20some%20part%20of%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20percentage%20of%20families%20who%20said%20they%20will%20use%20air%20purifiers%20has%2C%20however%2C%20gone%20up%20from%2018%25%20to%2023%25%20in%20two%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730487240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fuk7oaaho_delhi-air-quality_625x300_01_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F7-in-10-families-have-at-least-1-person-suffering-delhi-pollution-survey-6924272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20skyrocketing%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%20is%20directly%20impacting%20people's%20health%2C%20with%2069%25%20of%20families%20in%20the%20capital%20and%20NCR%20reporting%20at%20least%20one%20person%20suffering%2C%20a%20survey%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F7-in-10-families-have-at-least-1-person-suffering-delhi-pollution-survey-6924272%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20new%20way%20for%20Russia%20to%20c