es-connectivity-legacy-in-olympic-host-cities-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econnectivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20its%20stadium%2C%20Selhurst%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20when%20Vodafone%20approached%20Shared%20Access%20to%20help%20build%20a%20system%20for%20the%20stadium%20that%20ensures%20great%20service%20even%20when%20all%2030%2C000%20fans%20are%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-olympics-internet-connection-5g-mobile-technology-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euse%20their%20phones%20at%20once%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Crystal%20Palace%20team%20came%20to%20us%20for%20help%20supporting%20a%20specific%20cohort%20of%20fans%3A%20those%20with%20visual%20impairments.%20In%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.givevision.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGiveVision%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20were%20working%20on%20deploying%20headsets%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5g-tech-innovations-behind-paris-olympic-games-connectivity-timeline-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estream%20live%20match%20footage%3C%2Fa%3E%20directly%20to%20fans%20with%20partial%20sight%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20sit%20anywhere%20in%20the%20stadium%20but%20see%20every%20moment%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20pitch%20action%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20needed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5g-advanced-standalone-6g-qualcomm-huawei-mwc-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efaster%20connectivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a62d967b-58dc-4173-a02e-13c9a124d3fe%5C%22%3EThe%20existing%20networks%20weren't%20cutting%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20coming%20to%20us%2C%20the%20team%20working%20on%20the%20project%20tried%20running%20the%20headsets%20over%20WiFi%2C%20but%20there%20was%20too%20much%20latency.%20People%20using%20the%20headsets%20experienced%20everything%20on%20a%20slight%20delay%2C%20with%20the%20fans%20around%20them%20reacting%20to%20something%20on%20the%20field%20before%20they%20could%20see%20the%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%204G%20network%20that%20we'd%20previously%20deployed%20with%20Vodafone%2C%20and%20even%20public%205G%20networks%2C%20weren't%20going%20to%20do%20the%20job.%20Public%20networks%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20firewalls%20and%20protocols%20that%20create%20additional%20delays%2C%20such%20as%20the%20need%20for%20data%20to%20travel%20from%20the%20stadium%20to%20the%20core%20network%20of%20a%20mobile%20operator%20outside%20the%20stadium%20and%20then%20back%20to%20the%20user.%20It's%20also%20difficult%20because%20the%20number%20of%20other%20users%20using%20the%20network%20inside%20the%20venue%20slows%20things%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20decided%20to%20install%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-private-wireless-connectivity-changing-airport-experience-aviation-mwc-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%205G%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20on-site%20core%20in%20the%20stadium.%20This%20allows%20for%20fully%20enclosed%20connectivity%20within%20the%20venue%2C%20avoiding%20external%20data%20transfer%20and%20eliminating%20the%20security-protocol%20challenges%20of%20major%20mobile-network%20operators.%20It%20provides%20nearly%20instantaneous%20performance%2C%20with%20faster%20speeds%20than%204G%20and%20even%20purer%205G%20speeds%20than%20most%20public%20users%20experience.%20Additionally%2C%20because%20the%20club%20has%20total%20control%20over%20who%20can%20use%20the%20network%2C%20it%20can%20ensure%20all%20the%20bandwidth%20goes%20to%20these%20headsets%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2021%2C%20we%20officially%20launched%20the%20program%2C%20making%20Crystal%20Palace%20FC%20the%20first%20football%20club%20in%20the%20world%20to%20offer%20a%20permanent%20vision-enhancement%20system%20at%20its%20stadium%20for%20fans%20with%20sight%20impairments.%20Sinc