22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Bal%2C%20One%20Of%20India's%20Top%20Fashion%20Designers%2C%20Dies%20Of%20Cardiac%20Arrest%20At%2063%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERohit%20Bal%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20renowned%20fashion%20designers%2C%20has%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2063.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20of%20the%20designer%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Bal%20was%20in%20the%20ICU%20a%20week%20before%20his%20last%20show%20in%20October.%20He%20was%20discharged%20and%20then%20admitted%20to%20the%20Aashlok%20Hospital%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20where%20he%20died%20of%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20Instagram%2C%20the%20Fashion%20Design%20Council%20of%20India%20recalled%20the%20contributions%20of%20the%20fashion%20icon%2C%20who%20was%20also%20known%20as%20Gudda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20mourn%20the%20passing%20of%20Legendary%20designer%20Rohit%20Bal.%20He%20was%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20Fashion%20Design%20Council%20of%20India%20(FDCI).%20Known%20for%20his%20unique%20blend%20of%20traditional%20patterns%20with%20modern%20sensibilities%2C%20Bal's%20work%20redefined%20Indian%20fashion%2C%20and%20inspired%20generations.%20His%20legacy%20of%20artistry%2C%20and%20innovation%20along%20with%20forward%20thinking%20will%20live%20on%20in%20the%20fashion%20world.%20Rest%20in%20peace%20GUDDA%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20council%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFDCI%20president%20Sunil%20Sethi%20said%20the%20designer%20will%20be%20cremated%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20true%20that%20he%20has%20passed%20away.%20He%20had%20a%20cardiac%20arrest...%20heart%20failure.%20Rohit%20was%20a%20legend%2C%20we%20are%20completely%20shaken%20right%20now.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20work%20out%20details%20for%20the%20cremation%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sethi%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20Bal%20began%20his%20career%20in%201986%20and%20rose%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20the%20Indian%20fashion%20industry.%20He%20won%20'Designer%20of%20the%20Year'%20at%20the%20Indian%20Fashion%20Awards%20in%202006%2C%20and%20the%20Kingfisher%20Fashion%20Achievement%20Awards%20in%202001.%20He%20was%20also%20named%20the%20Lakme%20Grand%20Finale%20Designer%20in%202012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20battling%20illness%2C%20the%20designer%20made%20a%20return%20to%20the%20runway%20at%20the%20Lakme%20Fashion%20Week%20X%20FDCI%20grand%20finale%20last%20month%20where%20he%20showcased%20his%20collection%20'Kaaynaat%3A%20A%20Bloom%20in%20the%20Universe'.%20Lakme's%20brand%20ambassador%2C%20actor%20Ananya%20Panday%2C%20walked%20the%20ramp%20as%20the%20showstopper%20in%20a%20Rohit%20Bal%20signature%20ensemble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaymond%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Singhania%20mourned%20the%20death%20of%20the%20designer%2C%20calling%20him%20an%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20friend%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHeartbroken%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20an%20incredible%20friend.%20You%20brought%20so%20much%20light%2C%20laughter%2C%20and%20kindness%20into%20the%20lives%20of%20everyone%20around%20you.%20I'm%20grateful%20for%20every%20moment%20we%20shared%2C%20every%20laugh%2C%20every%20conversation.%20You'll%20be%20missed%20beyond%20words%2C%20but%20your%20spirit%20will%20live%20on%20in%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FuH1L2Z73i0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FuH1L2Z73i0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Gautam%20Singhania%20(%40SinghaniaGautam)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSinghaniaGautam%2Fstatus%2F1852370355983130975%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHeartbroken%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20an%20incredi