ying-over-puerto-rico-joke-you-dated-p-diddy%2Farticleshow%2F114853077.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114853077.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESocial%20media%20users%20asked%20her%20what%20she%20did%20for%20Puerto%20Rico%20and%20that%20her%20ex-boyfriend%20was%20Diddy%2C%20arrested%20for%20sex%20trafficking.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20were%20a%20regular%20at%20P.Diddy's%20parties%2C%20there's%20a%20100%25%20chance%20you'll%20endorse%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%26quot%3B%20Catturd%20posted.%20As%20LeBron%20James%20also%20endorsed%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20the%20detractors%20doubled%20down%20on%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20asked%20how%20all%20Diddy%20party%20attendees%20ended%20up%20in%20Kamala%20Harris%20campaign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjennifer-lopez-trolled-for-almost-crying-over-puerto-rico-joke-you-dated-p-diddy%2Farticleshow%2F114853077.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjennifer-lopez-trolled-for-almost-crying-over-puerto-rico-joke-you-dated-p-diddy%2Famp_articleshow%2F114853077.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjennifer-lopez-trolled-for-almost-crying-over-puerto-rico-joke-you-dated-p-diddy%2Famp_articleshow%2F114853077.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uddhav%20Sena%20Leader%20Charged%20For%20Derogatory%20Remark%20Against%20Shaina%20NC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20Mumbai%20South%20MP%20Arvind%20Sawant%20for%20his%20derogatory%20remark%20against%20Shaina%20NC%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20the%20Mumbadevi%20Assembly%20seat%20as%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Shaina%20NC%2C%20the%20Nagpada%20Police%20Station%20registered%20a%20first%20information%20report%20against%20Mr%20Sawant%2C%2072.%20The%20Maharashtra%20State%20Commission%20for%20Women%20has%20also%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20asked%20the%20police%20to%20probe%20the%20matter%20thoroughly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20some%20%3Cem%3E'maal'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(goods).%20I%20am%20a%20daughter%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20working%20dedicatedly%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20This%20is%20a%20crass%20comment%20by%20Sawant.%20I%20am%20a%20%3Cem%3E'mahila'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(woman)%2C%20not%20a%20%3Cem%3E'maal'%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Everyone%20knows%20that%20the%20Maha%20Vinash%20Aghadi%20(a%20play%20on%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20coalition)%20has%20no%20respect%20for%20women.%20The%20Mahayuti%20government%20is%20doing%20a%20lot%20for%20our%20womenfolk%2C%20like%20the%20'Ladki%20Bahin'%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shaina%20NC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20warned%20that%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Mumbadevi%20constituency%20would%20give%20an%20appropriate%20reply%20to%20Mr%20Sawant%2C%20who%2C%20she%20claimed%2C%20had%20won%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20using%20the%20name%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20earlier%2C%20owing%20to%20seat%20adjustments%2C%20Shaina%20NC%2C%2052%2C%20joined%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20was%20given%20the%20ticket%20for%20the%20prestigious%20Mumbadevi%20seat%2C%20where%20she%20is%20fighting%20three-term%20Congress%20MLA%20Amin%20Patel%20and%20BJP%20rebel%2C%20Atul%20H%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sawant%20had%20made%20the%20comments%20during%20a%20media%20interaction%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20ago%2C%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20Shaina%20NC's%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20his%20remark%2C%20Shaina%20NC%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20(BJP)%20had%20campaigned%20for%20him%20(Sawant)%20and%20he%20was%20elected%20on%20our%20strength.%20Ask%20him%20where%20he%20was%20from.%20I%20am%20a%20%3Cem%3E'laadli'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(beloved)%20daughter%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20I%20am%20working%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20city.%20I%20don't%20need%20any%20certificates%20from%20Mr%20Sawant%20or%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT).%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sawant%20later%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20a%20good%20equation%20with%20Shaina%20NC%20and%20she%20may%20have%20misunderstood%20his%20comment.%20%26quot%3BIt%20refers%20to%20'goods'%2C%20but%20she%20could%20have%20misinterpreted%20it.%20I%20had%20no%20such%20intentions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbadevi%20(earlier%20Umarkhadi)%20elected%20Amin%20Patel%20in%202009%20and%20then%20also%20during%20the%20BJP%20waves%20of%202014%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Shah%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20Khetwadi%20seat%2C%20could%20be%20a%20potential%20vote-cutter%20and%C2%A0talks%20are%20currently%20on%20to%20make%20him%20withdraw%20and%20bolster%20Shaina%20NC's%20prospects.%20Shaina%20NC's%20father%20was%20the%20late%20Sheriff%20of%20Mumbai%20Nana%20Chudasama%20and%20her%20mother%20is%20Munira%20Chudasama.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730469180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Ftdg7beog_shaina-nc_625x300_04_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-sawant-maal-remark-uddhav-sena-leader-charged-for-derogatory-remark-against-shaina-nc-6922186%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20Mumbai%20South%20MP%20Arvind%20Sawant%20for%20his%20derogatory%20remark%20against%20Shaina%20NC%2C%20the%20candidate%20from%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20for%20the%20Mumbadevi%20Assembly%20seat.%22%2C%22a