0Campaign%20after%20campaign%20they%20promise%20things%20to%20the%20people%2C%20which%20they%20also%20know%20they%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20deliver.%20Now%2C%20they%20stand%20badly%20exposed%20in%20front%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCheck%20any%20state%20where%20the%20Congress%20has%20governments%20today%20-%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20-%20the%20developmental%20trajectory%20and%20fiscal%20health%20is%20turning%20from%20bad%20to%20worse.%20Their%20so-called%20guarantees%20lie%20unfulfilled%2C%20which%20is%20a%20terrible%20deceit%20upon%20the%20people%20of%20these%20states.%20The%20victims%20of%20such%20politics%20are%20the%20poor%2C%20youngsters%2C%20farmers%20and%20women%2C%20who%20are%20not%20only%20denied%20the%20benefits%20of%20these%20promises%20but%20also%20see%20their%20existing%20schemes%20diluted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20promised%20many%20free%20schemes%20in%20Karnataka%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20However%2C%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar's%20comment%20on%20reviewing%20the%20Shakti%20free-travel%20scheme%20for%20women%20ran%20into%20a%20major%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20central%20leadership%20had%20to%20pull%20up%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20for%20even%20suggesting%20they'd%20review%20the%20scheme%2C%20while%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20had%20promised%20similar%20schemes%20in%20neighbouring%20Maharashtra%20where%20election%20is%20due%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Karnataka%2C%20Congress%20is%20busier%20in%20intra-party%20politics%20and%20loot%20instead%20of%20even%20bothering%20to%20deliver%20on%20development.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20they%20are%20also%20going%20to%20rollback%20existing%20schemes.%20In%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20salaries%20of%20government%20workers%20are%20not%20paid%20on