60-19e6a950e830.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce314y70lnpo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Their%20reports%20come%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20widespread%20violations%20highlighted%20by%20election%20monitors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A85%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce314y70lnpo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce314y70lnpo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce314y70lnpo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Newborn%20Was%20Thrown%20Off%20Bridge%20By%20Parents%2C%20Survived%2050%20Wounds%2C%20Animal%20Bite%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20a%20seven-day-old%20child%20was%20discovered%20stuck%20on%20a%20tree%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Hamirpur%20after%20he%20was%20thrown%20off%20a%20bridge%20by%20his%20parents.%20He%20had%20suffered%20at%20least%2050%20wounds%2C%20including%20a%20severe%20animal%20bite%20on%20his%20back%2C%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Kanpur%20where%20doctors%20were%20not%20sure%20whether%20he%20would%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20-%20named%20Krishna%20because%20he%20was%20found%20on%20Janmashtami%2C%20August%2026%20-%20may%20have%20started%20life%20being%20unwanted%2C%20but%20when%20he%20left%20the%20hospital%20completely%20cured%20two%20months%20later%2C%20not%20one%20eye%20was%20dry%20because%20every%20staff%20member%20had%20become%20attached%20to%20him%2C%20said%20a%20doctor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principal%20of%20the%20Lala%20Lajpat%20Rai%20Hospital%20in%20Kanpur%20(also%20known%20as%20Hallett%20Hospital)%20said%20the%20boy%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20institution%20by%20the%20district%20hospital%20in%20Hamirpur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20baby%20was%20thrown%20off%20a%20bridge%20in%20Rath%20near%20Hamirpur%20and%2C%20fortunately%2C%20he%20got%20stuck%20on%20a%20large%20tree.%20He%20suffered%20several%20wounds%20because%20of%20the%20fall.%20It%20appears%20he%20was%20also%20bitten%20by%20some%20crows%20and%20an%20animal%2C%20because%20he%20had%20a%20severe%20wound%20on%20his%20back.%20He%20was%20referred%20to%20us%20with%2050%20wounds%20in%20a%20critical%20condition%20by%20the%20Hamirpur%20district%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Sanjay%20Kala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStaff%20at%20the%20hospital%20said%20they%20named%20the%20child%20Krishna%2C%20because%20he%20was%20found%20on%20Janmashtami%2C%20and%20when%20he%20would%20cry%20in%20pain%2C%20the%20nurses%20would%20sing%20lullabies%20to%20him%20from%20a%20distance%20because%20the%20wounds%20all%20over%20his%20body%20prevented%20them%20from%20picking%20him%20up%20to%20pacify%20him.%20%26quot%3BHis%20pain%20and%20crying%20would%20bring%20tears%20to%20our%20eyes%2C%20and%20some%20of%20us%20sing%20to%20him%20or%20gently%20blow%20on%20his%20wounds%20to%20make%20him%20feel%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20nurse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kala%20said%20the%20boy's%20treatment%20took%20nearly%20two%20months%20and%20he%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20police%20and%20members%20of%20the%20child%20welfare%20committee%20on%20October%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20was%20leaving%20the%20hospital%2C%20all%20the%20staff%20members%20had%20tears%20in%20their%20eyes%20because%20they%20felt%20very%20attached%20to%20him%2C%20almost%20as%20if%20he%20was%20their%20own%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Kala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20were%20so%20attached%20to%20him%20in%20two%20months%2C%20I%20wonder%20how%20his%20parents%20could%20throw%20him%20off%20a%20bridge.%20Even%20if%20they%20did%20not%20want%20him%2C%20they%20could%20leave%20him%20at%20a%20hospital%20or%20in%20front%20of%20a%20temple%20or%20mosque.%20That%20way%2C%20he%20would%20have%20at%20least%20not%20got%20hurt%20or%20bitten%20by%20animals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshmi%2C%20a%20nurse%20from%20the%20neo-natal%20ICU%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20got%20better%2010-15%20days%20after%20he%20was%20admitted%2C%20we%20felt%20like%20taking%20him%20in%20our%20arms%2C%20but%20the%20wounds%20did%20not%20allow%20it.%20When%20we%20finally%20could%20do%20that%2C%20he%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20hospital.%20We%20are%20happy%20he%20has%20fully%20recovered%20and%20we%20hope%20he%20has%20a%20good%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Arun%20Agrawal)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730464800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F1jr7glp_baby-krishna-cured-up_625x300_01_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtar-pradesh-hamirpur-kanpur-newborn-was-thrown-off-bridge-by-parents-survived-50-wounds-animal-bite-6922094%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20August%2C%20a%20seven-day-old%20child%20was%20discovered%20stuck%20on%20a%20tree%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Hamirpur%20after%20he%20was%20thrown%20off%20a%20bridge%20by%20his%20parents.%20He%20had%20suffered%20at%20least%2050%20wounds%2C%20including%20a%20severe%20animal%20bite%20on%20his%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtar-pradesh-hamirpur-kanpur-newborn-was-thrown-off-bridge-by-parents-survived-50-wounds-animal-bite-6922094%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Vidya-Madhuri%20Not%20Out%20Of%20Step%20With%20The%20Spirit%20Of%20Bhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20something%20intrinsically%20and%20inevitably%20amusing%20in%20even%20the%20most%20frightening%20of%20ghost%20stories%20if%20the%20anything-goes%20on-screen%20antics%20of%20spectral%20apparitions%20are%20taken%20in%20the%20right%20spirit.%20That%20explains%20why%20horror-comedies%20usually%20have%20a%20such%20a%20committed%20constituency.%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20all%20its%20flaws%2C%20is%20unlikely%20to%20face%20a%20dearth%20of%20takers%20this%20Diwali%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20may%20not%20be%20as%20spooky%20as%20all-out%20horror%20flicks%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20-%20and%20that%20certainly%20isn't%20for%20want%20of%20trying%20-%20but%20its%20unbridled%20lunacy%20and%20spontaneous%20comic%20energy%20more%20than%20make%20up%20for%20what%20it%20lacks%20as%20a%20movie%20that%20is%20seeking%20to%20scare%20the%20audience%20out%20of%20their%20wits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20first%20two%20films%2C%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20mispronounces%20Manjulika%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20ways%20and%20degrees%20and%20gets%20away%20with%20it.%20That%20is%20one%20guessing%20game%20that%20this%20critic%20has%20always%20played%20with%20the%20entries%20of%20the%20franchise.%20Each%20time%20the%20name%20of%20the%20alleged%20vengeful%20phantom%20is%20mentioned%2C%20it%20sounds%20different.%20Nobody%20seems%20to%20have%20ever%20bothered%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20the%20right%20enunciation%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FXtzTLgt4Ndk%3Fsi%3D7x0WcLrb2qF6_xWE%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20instalment%2C%20as%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20audience%20is%20asked%20to%20spot%20who%2C%20what%20and%20where%20Manjulika%20is.%20It%20isn't%20until%20the%20very%20end%20of%20the%20film%20that%20the%20secret%20is%20revealed%20and%20it%20isn't%20what%20we%20expect%20it%20to%20be.%20In%20that%20regard%2C%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20catch%20us%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mispronunciation%20of%20a%20proper%20noun%20is%20but%20a%20minor%20drawback%20in%20a%20film%20that%20thinks%20nothing%20of%20indulging%20in%20a%20merciless%20mutilation%20of%20the%20Bengali%20language.%20The%20onslaught%20never%20stops%20because%20every%20character%20in%20the%20plot%20has%20a%20shot%20at%20it%20and%20comes%20up%20way%2C%20way%20short%20of%20phonetic%20accuracy.%20But%20for%20large%20swathes%20of%20the%20film's%20audience%20that%20drawback%20will%20hardly%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20%3Cem%3EAami%20je%20tomaar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20is%20of%20course%20a%20musical%20leitmotif%20that%20has%20survived%20all%20these%20years%2C%20one%20of%20the%20characters%20in%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%3C%2Fem%3E%20hums%20the%20Tagore%20song%20%3Cem%3EAami%20chini%20go%20chini%20tomare%20ogo%20bideshini%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0without%20anybody%20around%20bothering%20to%20reveal%20the%20provenance%20of%20the%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20wildly%20erratic%20in%20quality%20but%20notwithstanding%20its%20many%20obvious%20failings%2C%20it%20is%20way%20better%20than%20any%20of%20the%20hyper-masculine%20actioners%20that%20open%20in%20our%20multiplexes%20(and%20on%20the%20streaming%20platforms)%20week%20after%20week%20and%20revel%20in%20glorifying%20insatiable%20bloodlust%20expressed%20through%20innumerable%20means.%20Give%20us%20the%20harmless%20silliness%20of%20the%20BB3%20kind%20any%20day.%20It%20does%20not%20do%20as%20much%20harm%20as%20big%20screen%20violence%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20prelude%20in%20which%20we%20see%20a%20dancer%20turn%20into%20an%20angry%20ghost%20after%20being%20dragged%20away%20mid-performance%20from%20a%20royal%20court%20and%20burnt%20at%20the%20stake%20in%20a%20part%20of%20Bengal%20two%20centuries%20ago%2C%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20scripted%20by%20Aakash%20Kaushik%20(who%20co-wrote%20the%20previous%20instalment%20as%20well)%20and%20helmed%20by%20returning%20director%20Anees%20Bazmee%2C%20wastes%20no%20time%20at%20all%20in%20plunging%20into%20the%20mad%2C%20mad%2C%20mad%20world%20of%20'ghostbuster'%20Ruhaan%20(Kartik%20Aaryan).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalled%20Rooh%20Baba%20by%20his%20clientele%2C%20Ruhaan%20is%20a%20fraudulent%20exorcist%20who%20plies%20his%20trade%20in%20present-day%20Kolkata%20in%20the%20company%20of%20his%20lackey%20Tillu%20(Arun%20Kushwah).%20He%20claims%20to%20be%20endowed%20with%20the%20power%20to%20communicate%20with%20ghosts%20but%20is%20scared%20of%20rodents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20and%20Tillu%2C%20who%20faints%20at%20the%20slightest%20sign%20of%20danger%2C%20go%20about%20conning%20the%20gullible%2C%20they%20are%20pulled%20into%20a%20con%20that%20is%20much%20bigger%20than%20the%20ones%20that%20they%20perpetrate%20on%20their%20unsuspecting%20and%20gullible%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooh%20Baba%2C%20at%20the%20exhortation%20of%20Meera%20(Triptii%20Dimri)%20and%20her%20maternal%20uncle%20(Rajesh%20Sharma)%2C%20ends%20up%20in%20a%20haunted%20palace%20that%20has%20not%20been%20inhabited%20for%20many%20decades.%20The%20pauperised%20royal%20family%20headed%20by%20a%20maharaja%20(Vijay%20Raaz)%2C%20lives%20in%20the%20cattle%20shed%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%20mansion%20because%20that%20is%20all%20they%20can%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20emaciated%20cow%20gives%20no%20milk%2C%20every%20tube%20of%20toothpaste%20is%20made%20to%20last%20forever%20and%20the%20suspected%20presence%20of%20a%20ghost%20makes%20the%20sprawling%20property%20unsaleable.%20The%20first%20half%20of%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20breezy%20enough%20to%20pass%20muster%20as%20Rooh%20Baba%20worms%20his%20way%20into%20Meera's%20heart%20and%20wins%20over%20her%20family.%20But%20the%20film's%20flirtation%20with%20harmless%20inanity%20can%20go%20only%20this%20far%20and%20no%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20hilarity%20is%20replaced%20by%20a%20serious%20confrontation%20between%20the%20mortals%20who%20live%20in%20the%20house%20and%20the%20dead%20denizens%20who%20still%20hover%20behind%20locked%20doors%2C%20the%20film%20loses%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20its%20zing.%20It%20looks%20for%20ways%20-%20but%20largely%20in%20vain%20-%20to%20stay%20afloat%20on%20a%20merry%20mix%20of%20outlandish%20claptrap%20and%20the%20undeniable%20combined%20allure%20of%20Madhuri%20Dixit%2C%20who%20makes%20her%20entry%20in%20the%20final%20pre-interval%20scene%2C%20and%20Vidya%20Balan%2C%20who%20arrives%20on%20the%20scene%20much%20earlier%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20professional%20restorer%20of%20heritage%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20acting%20in%20the%20first%20half%20is%20mainly%20of%20a%20physical%20nature.%20It%20borders%20on%20slapstick%20and%20banter.%20But%20once%20Dixit%20and%20Balan%20(who%20is%20back%20in%20the%20BB%20world%20after%20all%20of%2017%20years)%20go%20toe%20to%20toe%2C%20their%20eyes%2C%20their%20dancing%20skills%20and%20emotive%20acumen%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20talking%2C%20raising%20the%20stakes%20in%20the%20bargain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20that%20the%20two%20seasoned%20performers%2C%20who%2C%20as%20the%20whole%20wide%20world%20knows%2C%20face%20off%20in%20a%20dance%20set-piece%2C%20one%20dressed%20in%20the%20manner%20of%20a%20Kathak%20performer%2C%20the%20other%20in%20a%20Bharatanatyam%20dancer's%20costume%2C%20aren't%20drawn%20into%20bouts%20of%20excess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20is%20never%20out%20of%20step%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20film%20even%20when%20they%20are%20mindful%20of%20not%20letting%20the%20maddening%20whirligig%20that%20the%20film%20is%20sweep%20them%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20an%20array%20of%20exceptionally%20gifted%20comic%20actors%20who%20provide%20the%20male%20lead%20all%20the%20support%20that%20he%20needs%20when%20the%20film%20begins%20to%20flag.%20Vijay%20Raaz%20is%20terrific%20as%20always%2C%20and%20so%20is%20the%20inimitable%20Sanjay%20Mishra.%20Not%20far%20behind%20the%20two%20are%20Rajesh%20Sharma%2C%20Rajpal%20Yadav%20and%20Ashwini%20Kalsekar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20evident%20that%20Kartik%20Aaryan%20has%20got%20the%20hang%20of%20the%20weird%20and%20disorienting%20house%20of%20mirrors%20that%20is%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%3C%2Fem%3E.%20His%20star%20turn%20is%20a%20repeat%20act%20that%20promises%20a%20box-office%20outcome%20that%20could%20be%20on%20par%20with%20what%20%3Cem%3EBhool%20Bhulaiyaa%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20yielded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730464560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fv37ls6b_vidya-_625x300_01_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbhool-bhulaiyaa-3-review-vidya-balan-and-madhuri-dixit-are-never-out-of-step-with-the-spirit-of-the-film-2-5-stars-6922105%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203%20Review%3A%20Kartik%20Aaryan's%20star%20turn%20is%20a%20repeat%20act%20that%20promises%20a%20box-office%20outcome%20that%20could%20be%20on%20par%20with%20what%20Bhool%20Bhulaiyaa%202%20yielded.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbhool-bhulaiyaa-3-review-vidya-balan-and-madhuri-dixit-are-never-out-of-step-with-the-spirit-of-the-film-2-5-stars-6922105%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20US%20Elections%3A%20When%20The%20Great%20American%20Dream%20Turns%20Nightmare%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Frdakscf8_kamala-harris-and-donald-trump_625x300_22_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20and%20fair%20elections%20in%20democratic%20societies%20reveal%20the%20spirit%20of%20a%20nation%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20United%20States%20with%20its%20extended%20election%20cycles.%20On%20the%20eve%20of%20a%20pivotal%20vote%2C%20what%20is%20the%20public%20mood%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20influential%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20were%20to%20capture%20the%20prevailing%20sentiment%20in%20the%20U.S.%20as%20election%20day%20approaches%2C%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bblue%20funk%26quot%3B.%20The%20atmosphere%20is%20saturated%20with%20anxiety%2C%20division%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20foreboding.%20With%20near-total%20polarisation%20and%20rising%20intolerance%20fuelled%20by%20Donald%20Trump's%20militant%20campaign%20style%2C%20this%20election%20is%20viewed%20with%20unprecedented%20worry%2C%20unhappiness%2C%20and%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20nine%20in%2010%20voters%20believe%20America%20will%20suffer%20lasting%20harm%20if%20their%20side%20loses.%20Close%20to%2060%25%20of%20Kamala%20Harris%20supporters%20report%20feeling%20%26quot%3Bfrightened%26quot%3B%20about%20a%20Trump%20victory%3B%2047%25%20of%20Trump%20supporters%20feel%20similarly%20about%20a%20Harris%20win.%20More%20than%20half%20of%20voters%20anticipate%20potential%20violence%20after%20the%20election%2C%20and%2053%25%20expect%20the%20country's%20divisions%20to%20deepen%20regardless%20of%20the%20outcome.%20Alarmingly%2C%20one%20in%20five%20Americans%20would%20consider%20resorting%20to%20violence%20to%20achieve%20political%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20Are%20Fed%20Up%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScott%20Evans%2C%2064%2C%20an%20early%20voter%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20expressed%20his%20disillusionment%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20I%20live%20in%20a%20country%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20in%20anymore.%26quot%3B%20Madison%20Bates%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20student%2C%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BCivil%20warpeople%20against%20the%20government.%20I%20definitely%20think%20if%20Trump%20doesn't%20get%20in%2C%20that's%20what%20could%20happen.%20People%20are%20fed%20up.%20You%20see%20it%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20grimness%20is%20evident%20across%20public%20opinion%20metrics.%20Six%20in%2010%20voters%20feel%20the%20country%20is%20on%20the%20wrong%20track.%20Over%20half%20say%20they%20are%20worse%20off%20than%20four%20years%20ago.%20In%20swing%20states%2C%20seven%20in%2010%20voters%20believe%20the%20political%20and%20economic%20systems%20require%20substantial%20change%20or%20even%20a%20complete%20overhaul%2C%20and%20they%20perceive%20the%20economy%20as%20rigged%20to%20benefit%20the%20wealthy%20and%20powerful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public's%20view%20of%20politics%20and%20politicians%20is%20%26quot%3Bunrelentingly%20negative%26quot%3B.%20More%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20respondents%20(28%25)%20view%20both%20major%20parties%20unfavourably%2C%20and%2063%25%20have%20little%20or%20no%20confidence%20in%20the%20political%20system's%20future.%20It's%20no%20surprise%20a%20nonpartisan%20group%20has%20labelled%20the%20American%20electorate%20an%20%26quot%3Bexhausted%20majority%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Americans%20Think%20About%20The%20Economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20politics%2C%20perception%20often%20becomes%20reality%2C%20especially%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20the%20economyvoters'%20top%20concern.%20Only%205%25%20of%20Americans%20rate%20the%20current%20economy%20as%20%26quot%3Bexcellent%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%2C%20while%2051%25%20believe%20it's%20in%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bterrible%26quot%3B%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReal%20disposable%20personal%20income%2C%20essentially%20take-home%20pay%2C%20has%20been%20stagnant%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20With%20the%20cost%20of%20essentials%20up%2020%25%20during%20this%20period%2C%20and%20housing%2C%20child%20care%2C%20and%20health%20care%20costs%20still%20climbing%2C%20affordability%20is%20a%20significant%20concern%2C%20with%20many%20blaming%20the%20Biden-Harris%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20is%20particularly%20severe%20on%20the%2060%25%20of%20voters%20without%20a%20college%20degree.%20In%201980%2C%20blue-collar%20workers%20earned%20almost%2010%25%20more%20than%20the%20national%20average%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20support%20families%2C%20buy%20homes%2C%20take%20vacations%2C%20and%20send%20their%20children%20to%20college.%20Forty%20years%20later%2C%20their%20inflation-adjusted%20income%20is%20stagnant%2C%20and%20they%20now%20make%2010%25%20less%20than%20the%20average%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnionisation%20rates%20have%20historically%20been%20highest%20in%20the%20swing%20states%20of%20the%20MidwestMichigan%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20and%20Pennsylvaniawhere%20organised%20labour%20once%20provided%20a%20premium%20on%20wages.%20With%20the%20decline%20in%20unionised%20manufacturing%20jobs%2C%20incomes%20have%20fallen%20relative%20to%20other%20sectors%2C%20leaving%20many%20susceptible%20to%20the%20MAGA%20narrative%20that%20they%20are%20victims%20in%20a%20zero-sum%20economy%20where%20immigrants%20and%20women%20gain%20at%20their%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Nuanced%20Reality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20U.S.%20economy%20is%20more%20nuanced%20and%20less%20grim.%20While%20prices%20rose%20about%2020%25%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20pandemic%20through%202023%2C%20the%20median%20worker's%20hourly%20wages%20rose%20by%20over%2026%25.%20From%202019%20to%202023%2C%20wages%20for%20the%20lowest-paid%20decile%20of%20workers%20grew%20four%20times%20faster%20than%20those%20for%20middle-class%20earners%2C%20and%20over%2010%20times%20faster%20than%20for%20the%20wealthiest%20decile.%20Pay%20for%20workers%20under%2025%20has%20also%20increased%20twice%20as%20fast%20as%20for%20older%20workers.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bcollege%20wage%20premium%26quot%3Bthe%20pay%20gap%20between%20those%20with%20and%20without%20a%20college%20degreev%20has%20fallen%20to%20its%20lowest%20level%20in%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve's%20Survey%20of%20Consumer%20Finances%2C%20conducted%20every%20three%20years%2C%20shows%20that%20from%202019%20to%202022%2C%20the%20net%20worth%20of%20the%20median%20US%20household%20rose%20by%2037%25%2C%20from%20about%20%24141%2C000%20to%20%24192%2C000%2C%20adjusted%20for%20inflation.%20This%20is%20the%20largest%20three-year%20increase%20on%20record%20since%201989.%20Every%20income%20group%20saw%20significant%20net%20worth%20gains%2C%20with%20the%20largest%20increases%20seen%20among%20lower-income%2C%20middle-class%2C%20Black%2C%20Latino%2C%20and%20younger%20households%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20modest%20decrease%20in%20wealth%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20picture%20remains%20complex%2C%20with%20significant%20improvements%20for%20many%20alongside%20persistent%20affordability%20challenges%20for%20others%2C%20shaping%20a%20conflicted%20national%20mood%20as%20voters%20head%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0offers%20some%20telling%20statistics%20in%20its%20recent%20cover%20story%20on%20the%20US%20economy%20titled%20%3Cem%3EThe%20World's%20Envy%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Average%20wages%20in%20America's%20poorest%20state%2C%20Mississippi%2C%20are%20higher%20than%20the%20averages%20in%20Britain%2C%20Canada%20and%20Germany.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20average%20American%20worker%20will%20generate%20about%20%24171%2C000%20in%20economic%20output%2C%20representing%20a%2070%25%20increase%20in%20productivity%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20The%20US%20accounts%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20global%20private-sector%20investment%20in%20AI.%20As%20the%20paper%20concluded%3A%20%26quot%3BAn%20economy%20with%20an%20unemployment%20rate%20of%204%25%20and%20a%20per-person%20GDP%C2%A0of%20%2485%2C000%20does%20not%20have%20to%20be%20made%20great%20again%3B%20it%20is%20great.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Immigration%20Gambit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20knows%20that%20immigration%20places%20the%20Biden-Harris%20administration%20on%20slippery%20ground%2C%20which%20is%20why%20he%20has%20made%20it%20his%20leading%20campaign%20issue%2C%20sidelining%20his%20advisers'%20calls%20to%20prioritise%20the%20economy.%20The%20administration%20kept%20the%20borders%20relatively%20open%20until%20this%20June%2C%20when%20enforcement%20measures%20finally%20tightened.%20Harris%20has%20attempted%20to%20shift%20some%20blame%20to%20Trump%2C%20citing%20his%20role%20in%20blocking%20a%20bipartisan%20bill%20earlier%20in%202024%20that%20would%20have%20enforced%20stricter%20policies%20sooner.%20But%20this%20strategy%20has%20not%20gained%20traction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20net%20immigration%20to%20the%20US%20has%20been%20the%20highest%20globally%2C%20with%202.6%20million%20immigrants%20in%202022%20and%203.3%20million%20in%202023.%20Since%20Biden%20took%20office%2C%20nine%20million%20immigrants%20have%20entered%20the%20country%2C%20roughly%20half%20of%20them%20undocumented.%20Only%20one%20in%20five%20Americans%20find%20these%20numbers%20acceptable%3B%2032%25%20believe%20the%20US%20should%20%26quot%3Bslow%20the%20influx%26quot%3B%20of%20immigrants%2C%20and%2016%25%20favour%20%26quot%3Binstituting%20a%20moratorium%20on%20new%20arrivals%26quot%3B.%20One-third%20say%20America%20should%20%26quot%3Bclose%20the%20border%20immediately%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20rallied%20his%20base%2C%20particularly%20the%20MAGA%20contingent%2C%20against%20undocumented%20immigrants%2C%20inflating%20their%20number%20to%20between%2020-25%20million%2C%20though%20the%20actual%20figure%20is%20likely%20about%20half%20that.%20He%20has%20pledged%20to%20undertake%20mass%20deportations%20if%20elected.%20Over%2060%25%20of%20Americans%2C%20including%2053%25%20of%20Hispanics%2C%20say%20they%20support%20a%20programme%20to%20deport%20undocumented%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmigration%20has%20become%20a%20flashpoint%2C%20underscoring%20deep%20cultural%20divides%20in%20the%20U.S.%20Studies%20indicate%20that%20immigrants'%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20way%20of%20life%26quot%3B%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20longstanding%20communitiesmainly%20among%20older%2C%20non-college-educated%2C%20working-class%2C%20predominantly%20white%20populations%20from%20European%20backgrounds%2C%20as%20well%20as%20religious%20and%20rural%20Americans.%20These%20groups%20feel%20increasingly%20alienated%20from%20shifting%20social%20and%20moral%20values%2C%20believing%20the%20elite%20is%20complicit%20in%20eroding%20traditional%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReligion%20And%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20declining%20religiosity%2C%20nearly%20two-thirds%20of%20Americans%20identify%20themselves%20as%20Christian%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Public%20Religion%20Research%20Institute.%20In%20the%201980s%2C%20white%20Christians%2C%20especially%20%26quot%3Bborn-again%26quot%3B%20evangelicals%20(who%20make%20up%2014%25%20of%20the%20population)%2C%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20Republican%20voting%20bloc.%20Today%2C%2060%25%20of%20Protestants%2C%20including%208%20out%20of%2010%20white%20evangelicals%2C%20support%20Trump.%20Political%20scientist%20Paul%20Djupe's%20surveys%20suggest%20that%2018%25%20of%20Americans%20strongly%20agree%20that%20modern-day%20prophets%20continue%20to%20reveal%20God's%20plans%20for%20humanity.%20Among%20these%2C%20three-fifths%20believe%20the%20upcoming%20election%20may%20be%20the%20last%20chance%20to%20%26quot%3Brid%20America%20of%20demonic%20influence%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20two-fifths%20think%20a%20civil%20war%20might%20be%20necessary%20to%20%26quot%3Bset%20the%20country%20back%20on%20the%20right%20path%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGender%20is%20another%20widening%20societal%20divide.%20Men%20and%20women's%20political%20views%20are%20diverging%20sharply%2C%20with%20a%20recent%20poll%20showing%20men%20favouring%20Trump%20by%20four%20points%20and%20women%20favouring%20Harris%20by%2010.%20Nearly%20seven%20in%2010%20Tr