tish%20Rana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20no%20brainers%20would%20have%20been%20maybe%2010%20or%2011%20players%2C%20but%20trying%20to%20trim%20that%20down%20to%20six%20was%20very%20challenging%2C%20because%20it's%20about%20the%20players%20that%20you%20have%20built%20an%20equation%20with%20and%20who%20have%20done%20fantastic%20for%20KKR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSunil%20has%20been%20with%20us%20for%2012%20years%20while%20Andre%20has%20been%20with%20us%20for%2010%20years.%20Varun%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20KKR%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20since%202019%20and%20Rinku%20as%20well%20has%20been%20with%20for%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20since%202018.%20Harshit%20has%20been%20with%20the%20team%20for%20three%20years%20while%20Ramandeep%20came%20in%20last%20year%20and%20really%20made%20a%20big%20impact.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20good%20combination.%20And%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20some%20of%20the%20thinking%20around%20how%20you%20want%20to%20handle%20the%20auction%20also%20came%20into%20play%2C%20but%20we%20thought%20that%20this%20was%20a%20really%20good%20combination%20for%20us.%20And%2C%20obviously%20leaving%20out%20some%20of%20the%20players%20is%20never%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mysore%20in%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcess%20of%20retention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20process%20of%20conversations%20they%20had%20with%20the%20players%20before%20finalising%20their%20retention%20picks.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20think%20our%20approach%20has%20always%20been%20to%20maintain%20transparency%20and%20have%20proper%20conversations%20with%20everyone.%20I've%20not%20really%20had%20conversations%20with%20the%20six%20we%20have%20retained%2C%20but%20I%20have%20engaged%20in%20conversations%20with%20the%20ones%20we%20couldn't%20retain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20obviously%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20some%20of%20the%20narratives%20that%20have%20been%20going%20around.%20It's%20sufficient%20to%20say%20that%2C%20we%20always%20engage%20in%20talks%20with%20everyone%20and%20most%20people%20understand%20our%20position.%20In%20almost%20all%20cases%2C%20everyone%20asks%20if%20there%20is%20a%20way%20we%20can%20retain%20them%2C%20but%20they%20also%20understand%20why%20we%20can't%2C%20and%20hopefully%2C%20somewhere%20our%20paths%20will%20cross%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20also%2C%20something%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20mind%20is%20that%20retention%20is%20not%20a%20one%20way%20street.%20It%20is%20always%20something%20that%20has%20to%20be%20mutually%20agreed%20upon.%20So%2C%20sometimes%20mutual%20agreements%20happen%20but%20we%20also%20have%20to%20be%20respectful%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20player%20may%20choose%20to%20go%20the%20other%20way%2C%20And%2C%20it's%20a%20little%20tough%20when%20that%20situation%20happens%2C%20but%20that%20happens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20KKR%20having%20a%20purse%20of%20INR%2051%20crore%2C%20Mysore%20also%20talked%20how%20the%20mega%20auction%20would%20be%20a%20different%20scenario%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20nature%20of%20the%20rules%20this%20year%20is%20that%20it%20will%20be%20challenging%20for%20everyone%20in%20different%20ways.%20In%20our%20case%2C%20after%20retaining%206%20players%20we%20go%20into%20the%20auction%20with%2051%20crores%20and%20no%20RTMs%20(Right-To-Match%20Card).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20there%20may%20be%20some%20other%20team%20who%20retains%20none%20or%20very%20few%2C%20and%20they%20come%20in%20with%20more%20money.%20But%20their%20challenge%20is%20to%20build%20a%20squad%2C%20a%20full%20squad.%20Our%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20complete%20our%20squad%2C%20so%20each%20one%20will%20come%20with%20their%20own%20strategies%2C%20and%20everyone%20is%20very%20experienced.%20I've%20been%20part%20of%2014%20auctions%20with%20this%20being%20the%2015th%20one%2C%20but%20it%20n