anxiety%20without%20knowing%20what%20it%20was.%20He%20experienced%20panic%20attacks%20and%20breakdowns%20at%20work%20and%20home%20but%20kept%20pushing%20himself.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20out%20of%20bed%2C%20and%20often%20found%20himself%20sweating%20uncontrollably.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20fragile%20and%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20breaking%2C%20leading%20to%20self%20doubt.%20I%20used%20to%20think%20that%20I%20was%20a%20terrible%20employee.%20Sometimes%2C%20during%20meetings%2C%20I%20would%20have%20panic%20attacks%20and%20had%20to%20go%20out%20to%20gather%20myself%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20I%20just%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20was%20happening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20he%20experienced%20a%20massive%20anxiety%20attack%20and%20feared%20something%20was%20wrong%20with%20his%20heart.%20Like%20many%2C%20Nikhil%20experienced%20his%20anxiety%20manifest%20as%20physical%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20heart%20raced%20constantly.%20I%20felt%20breathless%2C%20as%20if%20I%20were%20on%20a%20plane%20experiencing%20turbulence%2C%20convinced%20everything%20was%20about%20to%20come%20crashing%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBattle%20with%20anxiety%3A%20Taking%20a%20career%20break%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20enduring%20these%20symptoms%20for%20nine%20months%2C%20he%20finally%20visited%20a%20doctor%20for%20a%20physical%20checkup.%20The%20doctor%20told%20him%20that%20he%20was%20fine%20physically%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20visit%20a%20psychiatrist.%20The%20psychiatrist%20prescribed%20medication%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290199%2Fviral-twitter-thread-by-aditya-verma-on-depression-diabetes-netflix-addiction%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuggested%20therapy.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimadri%20Sharma%2C%20a%20cou