20concerned%20about%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20By%20focusing%20on%20imparting%20hospitality%20skills%20along%20with%20basic%20education%20to%20the%20tribal%20people%20and%20families%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%2C%20she%20equips%20them%20with%20the%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20to%20become%20stewards%20of%20their%20environment.%20It%20is%20a%20reciprocal%20learning%20experience%2C%20where%20Padmaja%20and%20her%20team%20learn%20from%20the%20ancient%20wisdom%20of%20the%20tribal%20people%2C%20the%20true%20custodians%20of%20the%20land%20for%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurli%20Menon%2C%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EEnvironmentally%20Friendly%20Poetry%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20stayed%20at%20Bhagheera%E2%80%99s%20Camp%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20a%20month%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20only%20an%20ideal%20place%20to%20write%20poetry%20and%20connect%20with%20nature%2C%20but%20also%20inspiring%20to%20see%20a%20camp%20that%20is%20so%20self-sufficient.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20his%20visit%20in%202017%2C%20he%20has%20been%20a%20regular%20participant%20in%20the%20annual%20reforestation%20work%20at%20the%20camp%2C%20joining%20other%20dedicated%20environmentalists%20in%20their%20mission%20to%20rewild%20Jawai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20of%20community%20engagement%20and%20empowerment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Padmaja%20was%20a%20TEDx%20speaker%20at%20Bodhi%20International%20School%2C%20Jodhpur.%20During%20her%20talk%2C%20she%20shared%20the%20realities%20of%20depleting%20habitats.%20The%20students%20ended%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305478%2Fkerala-daily-wager-plants-trees-in-anganwadi-schools-wins-environment-award%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanting%20325%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20now%20cared%20for%20by%20Rewilding%20Jawai%2C%20under%20Bagheera%E2%80%99s%20Camp.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20with%20kids%20and%20young%20people%20is%20incredibly%20inspiring%20because%20they%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20active%20participation.%20This%20allows%20people%20like%20us%2C%20a%20non%20governmental%2C%20not%20for%20profit%20organisation%2C%20to%20continue%20doing%20what%20we%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Padmaja%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20worked%20with%20over%20500%20tribal%20people%20and%20has%20been%20widely%20recognised%20for%20her%20efforts.%20In%202017%2C%20Bagheera%E2%80%99s%20Camp%20was%20nominated%20for%20the%20Outlook%20Responsible%20Travel%20Awards%20and%20the%2014th%20UNWTO%20Awards%20for%20Innovation%20in%20Tourism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20998px)%20100vw%2C%20998px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-25-at-2.20.00-PM-1_11zon-1729864191.jpeg%3Ffit%3D998%252C748%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22998%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20leopard%20lounges%20on%20a%20rocky%20ledge%20in%20Jawai%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20safely%20observed%20from%20a%20distance%2C%20while%20two%20peacocks%20display%20their%20vibrant%20feathers%20nearby.%20This%20scene%20showcases%20the%20rich%20biodiversity%20of%20this%20stunning%20habitat.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-25-at-2.20.00-PM-1_11zon-1729864191.jpeg%3Fw%3D998%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20998w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-25-at-2.20.00-PM-1_11zon-1729864191.jpeg%3Fresize%3D300%252C225%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-25-at-2.20.00-PM-1_11zon-1729864191.jpeg%3Fresize%3D500%252C375%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-25-a