0a%20fundraising%20job%20that%20pays%20me%20Rs%2022%2C500%20a%20month.%20I%20invest%20regularly%20through%20Groww%20and%20have%20already%20saved%20Rs%2050%2C000.%20I%E2%80%99m%20pursuing%20a%20BA%20in%20Gender%20Studies%2C%20and%20once%20I%E2%80%99ve%20saved%20enough%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20chase%20my%20fashion%20dreams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20importantly%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20learnt%20to%20manage%20my%20anger%2C%20guide%20my%20siblings%2C%20and%20be%20a%20pillar%20of%20support%20for%20my%20family.%20From%20having%20no%20responsibilities%20at%2018%20to%20shouldering%20so%20many%20within%20just%20a%20year%2C%20I%20sometimes%20marvel%20at%20how%20much%20I%20am%20capable%20of%20handling!%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20quarter%2C%20we%20reconnect%20with%20our%20alumni%20to%20assess%20if%20they%20need%20any%20upskilling%20or%20if%20new%20job%20opportunities%20have%20arisen.%20It%E2%80%99s%20our%20way%20of%20ensuring%20their%20continued%20growth%20and%20success%2C%20even%20after%20they%E2%80%99ve%20transitioned%20out%20of%20our%20programme.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20know%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20never%20alone%20in%20this%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramya%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20foundation%20built%20on%20%E2%80%98CRAFT%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20WeLive%E2%80%99s%20philosophy%20lies%20a%20powerful%20acronym%3A%20CRAFT%20%E2%80%94%20Care%2C%20Respect%2C%20Affection%2C%20Freedom%2C%20and%20Trust.%20These%20guiding%20values%20shape%20every%20facet%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20mission%2C%20fostering%20a%20nurturing%20environment%20that%20transcends%20the%20basics%20of%20food%20and%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20many%20of%20these%20youths%2C%20this%20is%20not%20just%20their%20first%20job%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20first%20encounter%20with%20the%20world%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20care%20institutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains